{"tid":1256450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"DQ確認書殺入區議會選舉諮詢 今晚就係！！！","createTime":"2019-06-25T04:38:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T15:27:25.000Z","uid":54046,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1e76a3a0f952eb21f0307a8e76d2787bada47a86","tid":1256450,"uid":54046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T04:38:43.000Z","msg":"[緊急廣傳]<br />\nDQ確認書殺入區議會選舉諮詢 今晚就係！！！<br />\n<br />\n選舉事務處就修改「區議會選舉活動建議指引」做公眾諮詢，其中一項超重大修訂，就係為區議會選舉引入萬惡嘅「確認書」，等選舉主任可以隨意DQ參選人資格（見「指引」第三章第3.9(b)條）。<br />\n處方今晚（6月25日）會就修訂舉行公眾諮詢大會，既然我哋話要喺11月重奪區議會，就冇可能俾武器佢哋，DQ晒政府想封殺嘅人，等保皇黨自動當選！做個好公民，記得積極去發表意見！<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年6月25日<br />\n時間：晚上7時至9時<br />\n地點：鰂魚涌基利路1號鰂魚涌社區會堂<br />\n「區議會選舉活動建議指引」<br />\n全文： <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eac.hk/pdf/distco/2019dc/proposed_guideline/ch/dc_full_guide.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eac.hk%2Fpdf%2Fdistco%2F2019dc%2Fproposed_guideline%2Fch%2Fdc_full_guide.pdf&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443vQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=ef496b77\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eac.hk/pdf/distco/2019dc/proposed_guideline/ch/dc_full_guide.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"0e92ecc0d393f71757be7c5dceb26d1fb4e29a5c","tid":1256450,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T04:41:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7b0a300e4f93df44f3f3e5ad9f0dc7dedbce524f","tid":1256450,"uid":12149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T04:43:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ccaa3ecfe0290608cd2c854075e6cbec0d4b1c5","tid":1256450,"uid":11849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T04:43:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a40a34084df91885a78fb797f1b937d6da5492b","tid":1256450,"uid":110870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T04:44:46.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1d7fa3155303160fa23e45b870a10a072118fa97","tid":1256450,"uid":54046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-